dmca.title: Web DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.body:
Hi,

We are sorry to report that your members have posted images that breach the copyright of our World Guide sites.

Therefore, we wish to issue the following DMCA complaint;

1. MR. MARTIN TREASURE

2.The images copied are as follows:

http://crosscountryblogjudy.blogspot.co.uk/2011/06/edmonton.html
http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-dLhBgTchYEY/TewYdU7juXI/AAAAAAAAABQ/Igxc3RLWGaU/s1600/edmonton_map.jpg
http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-dLhBgTchYEY/TewYdU7juXI/AAAAAAAAABQ/Igxc3RLWGaU/s400/edmonton_map.jpg
http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-dLhBgTchYEY/TewYdU7juXI/AAAAAAAAABQ/Igxc3RLWGaU/s320/edmonton_map.jpg
http://crosscountryblogjudy.blogspot.co.uk/2011/06/vancouver.html
http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HAW1-sqb3r8/Tev77DHY0LI/AAAAAAAAAAc/WtHH5UpSGnw/s1600/banff.jpg
http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HAW1-sqb3r8/Tev77DHY0LI/AAAAAAAAAAc/WtHH5UpSGnw/s400/banff.jpg
http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HAW1-sqb3r8/Tev77DHY0LI/AAAAAAAAAAc/WtHH5UpSGnw/s320/banff.jpg
http://marialombardic.blogspot.co.uk/2011/07/map-of-new-jersey-cities.html
http://irevirimagensdeumviajante.blogspot.co.uk/2011/10/as-casas-de-new-port-rhode-island.html



3. The original images can be viewed here:

http://www.edmonton.world-guides.com/edmonton_maps.html
http://www.world-guides.com/images/edmonton/edmonton_map.jpg
http://www.banff.world-guides.com/banff_maps.html
http://www.world-guides.com/images/banff/banff.jpg
http://www.atlantic-city.world-guides.com/atlantic_city_maps.html
http://www.world-guides.com/images/atlantic_city/map1_atlantic_city.jpg
http://www.world-guides.com/images/new_jersey_nj/new_jersey_nj_state_map.jpg
http://www.newport.world-guides.com/newport_maps.html
http://www.world-guides.com/images/newport/newport_city_map.jpg



4.  Contact: [redacted] - director TravelSmart Ltd
Tel: +[redacted]
Email: info@world-guides.com
Address: [redacted], Frome, Somerset, England BA11 2DL

5. I have a good faith belief that use of the material in the manner complained of is not authorized by World Guides.

6. I hereby state under penalty of perjury that this information is accurate, and that I am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of the infringed materials.


Many thanks once again for your help, please advise if you require any further information.

I look forward to hearing from you shortly.

MARTIN
